RelatedSentence: KIDAL , Mali May 18 ( Reuters ) - Six Malian government officials and two civilians were murdered during an assault by Tuareg separatist rebels on a regional governor 's office in the northern town of Kidal , the country 's United Nations peacekeeping mission said on Sunday .
